- Jaffe, A., & Witten, E. "Quantum Yang-Mills Theory"
- Streater & Wightman (1964): "PCT, Spin and Statistics, and All That"
- Osterwalder & Schrader (1973, 1975): "Axioms for Euclidean Green's functions"
-/

