- `QuantumYangMillsTheory`: The complete structure of the QFT
- `TwoPointFunction`: The correlation function $\langle \phi(x) \phi(y) \rangle$

The problem asks us to show that the theory has a mass gap, either via the two-point function decaying exponentially or via the spectrum of the Hamiltonian.

