This file formalizes the Millennium Prize problem on the Yang-Mills existence and mass gap. This was the hardest conjecture to formalize for me as I didn't know basically any concepts and had to learn and debug a lot with Claude and LeanSearch and the Mathlib library + watch videos.

The problem asks to prove that:
